name: what you get?
description:
Head goldfish and body rat, we never know human nature will be like an animal or as human for a real, so what do you get for your life and your artworks? money? likes? or as a paradigm changer? cause our life looks like a fisherman, we never know what we get, fish, rubbish, crab, octopus, or mermaid maybe.
be consistent in your life and works.
